  <entry>
    <title>桌面语音助手</title>
    <link href="http://uerlink.github.io/2022/05/22/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B/"/>
    <id>http://uerlink.github.io/2022/05/22/%E5%AE%9E%E8%B7%B5%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%AD%E9%9F%B3%E5%8A%A9%E6%89%8B/</id>
    <published>2022-05-21T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-06-19T19:12:31.934Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="功能需求"><a href="#功能需求" class="headerlink" title="功能需求:"></a>功能需求:</h2><ul><li>语音控制台灯</li><li>语音控制….</li><li>将控制信息显示在oled屏幕上</li></ul><h2 id="问题"><a href="#问题" class="headerlink" title="问题"></a>问题</h2><p>以前也做个类似的控制(小爱同学+esp8266+继电器) 但是这个缺点太大了. 不能免唤醒词 必须联网, 控制延迟也很大. 而且不能自定义回答</p><h2 id="解决方案"><a href="#解决方案" class="headerlink" title="解决方案"></a>解决方案</h2><p>淘宝上买了一个语音控制的模块(<strong>SU-03T</strong>), 离线语音, 免唤醒, 响应时间很快. 完美符合我的要求. 在线编程自己生成sdk,和固件.</p><h3 id="思维导图"><a href="#思维导图" class="headerlink" title="思维导图"></a>思维导图</h3><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/ae497828b0434100830e9b1cef20bfdd.png#pic_center" alt="img" srcset="https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/05/qOHJw8.jpg" data-src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/ae497828b0434100830e9b1cef20bfdd.png#pic_center" class="lozad post-image"></p><h3 id="arduino代码"><a href="#arduino代码" class="headerlink" title="arduino代码"></a>arduino代码</h3><pre class="highlight"><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;Wire.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 引入驱动OLED0.96所需的库</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;Adafruit_GFX.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;Adafruit_SSD1306.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> SCREEN_WIDTH 128 <span class="comment">// 设置OLED宽度,单位:像素</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> SCREEN_HEIGHT 64 <span class="comment">// 设置OLED高度,单位:像素</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> OLED_RESET 4</span></span><br><span class="line">Adafruit_SSD1306 <span class="title function_">display</span><span class="params">(SCREEN_WIDTH, SCREEN_HEIGHT, &amp;Wire, OLED_RESET)</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;SoftwareSerial.h&gt;</span>  <span class="comment">//软串口库</span></span></span><br><span class="line">SoftwareSerial <span class="title function_">mySerial</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>)</span>; <span class="comment">////定义软串口，arduino的2号引脚作为RX，arduino的3号引脚作为TX，根据需要自行修改</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">setup</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Serial.begin(<span class="number">9600</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.begin(<span class="number">9600</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  display.begin(SSD1306_SWITCHCAPVCC, <span class="number">0x3C</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">loop</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    DataJC();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//------读取串口</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">DataJC</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (mySerial.available() &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) <span class="comment">//检测软串口是否有数据</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> val = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    val = mySerial.read();<span class="comment">//读出串数据</span></span><br><span class="line">    Serial.println(val);  <span class="comment">//从主串口打开出来</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (val == <span class="number">161</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;A1已开启&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      A1_on();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (val == <span class="number">162</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;A1已关闭&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      A1_off();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (val == <span class="number">17</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;响应&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      Emoji_1();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//表情:响应</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">Emoji_1</span><span class="params">()</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  display.clearDisplay();</span><br><span class="line">  display.setTextColor(WHITE);</span><br><span class="line">  display.setTextSize(<span class="number">4</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  display.setCursor(<span class="number">45</span>, <span class="number">10</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  display.print(<span class="string">&quot;Hi&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  display.display();</span><br><span class="line">  delay(<span class="number">1000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  display.clearDisplay();</span><br><span class="line">  display.setTextColor(WHITE);</span><br><span class="line">  display.setTextSize(<span class="number">4</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  display.setCursor(<span class="number">32</span>, <span class="number">10</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  display.print(<span class="string">&quot;o o&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  display.display();</span><br><span class="line">  delay(<span class="number">1000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//打开A1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">A1_on</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      display.clearDisplay();</span><br><span class="line">      display.setTextColor(WHITE);</span><br><span class="line">      display.setTextSize(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      display.setCursor(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">20</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      display.print(<span class="string">&quot;A1 &gt;&gt; on&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      display.display();</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">//delay(2000);</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//关闭A1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">A1_off</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      display.clearDisplay();</span><br><span class="line">      display.setTextColor(WHITE);</span><br><span class="line">      display.setTextSize(<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      display.setCursor(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">20</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      display.print(<span class="string">&quot;A1 &gt;&gt; off&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      display.display();</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">//delay(2000);</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//向软串口输出数据</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">send_cmd</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> cmd)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">char</span> mylist[<span class="number">9</span>]=&#123;<span class="number">0xAA</span>,<span class="number">0x55</span>,<span class="number">0x01</span>,<span class="number">0x01</span>,<span class="number">0x00</span>,<span class="number">0x00</span>,<span class="number">0x00</span>,<span class="number">0x55</span>,<span class="number">0xAA</span>&#125;;<span class="comment">//设置发送列表</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">//改变数值</span></span><br><span class="line">  mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">3</span>)] = cmd; </span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">0</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">1</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">2</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">3</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">4</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">5</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">6</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">7</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">  mySerial.write(mylist[(<span class="type">int</span>)(<span class="number">8</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
